Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真让人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋样 我的GExes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…觉得和高达有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相似 相似
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在乎小事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达Titus确实厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GExes也丝毫不落下风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 宇宙虽大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种手艺的机动战士工匠着实不多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出是一顶一的高手所造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁造了这台GExes？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别那么一本正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有约会邀请吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有魅力的男人真忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沃尔夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是麦德纳大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始移居殖民卫星后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经数百年宇宙时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争夺地球圈霸权的战争终于偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的时代似乎降临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平却如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的不明敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一颗殖民卫星化作宇宙的尘埃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将成为百年漫长战争的开端
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有正常一点的驾驶方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那就是麦德纳工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造GExes的牛逼大叔就住那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生 要撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到站了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小瞧前赛车手的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 军用机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未经联邦认可的设施进行改装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是违法的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 也有许多我这样的排队来买
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是看重这里老板的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是个出了名的倔脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 到时候别后悔跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想毁了我的工坊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事才急着来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意 进来吧沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉拉帕里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你这么惯着沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子才爬鼻子上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最经常损坏工坊是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次 让研制中的等离子炮爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁破了那么大一个窟窿以为我会不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉碰上老婆也没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没辙 没辙 没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这些 有东西想给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来工厂区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这里就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组装工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管不是军队的工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这么先进的设备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让爷爷看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有联邦军的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有从未见过的机型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还是经过整体改装的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能找到适合我的机动战士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合 适合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是玩具 谁允许你碰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎么带来这么一群吵吵闹闹的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对老爹的敬仰之情如滔滔江水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 让孩子们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全～是你个人爱好造的试作机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试作机？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给沃尔夫做机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他别提多激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能输给那个叫高达的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要造出更强更有型的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GExes果然是仿高达造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 GExes的品质完全无可挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅拥有高功率光束军刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大幅提升近身战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装卸式的盾牌还可以作为辅助装甲强化防御力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有了这些我感觉完全不输给高达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可动轴的转向速度方面高达完全占优
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机构关节的柔韧性和缓震性能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是高达的效率较高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明日野家的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样我有话想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这里的协调控制系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人为什么都那么傻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家这位更是特大号的机动战士傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿他没法子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我家老爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷是高达机械工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也说GExes的制造者是一顶一的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程师之间 有某些共通的语言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说 我也是被那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为某件事废寝忘食的样子迷上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么相亲相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说老爹 刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事让你在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你不说我都给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 UE的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这东西会在老爹机库里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请解释是怎么回事 麦德纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据回答 就算是老爹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事出有因的话请告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这台机动战士是受某位客户所托
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是 提升这东西的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个客户？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个客户是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 艾米莉 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一知道的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去大家都得翘辫子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦德纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请借给我们能用的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去用格纳库里的Shaldoll
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别轻敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙打算逃去外面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪里逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损失情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在确认中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先救人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上显示画面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过这么锋利的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我引诱它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去喊高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 听得见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和UE的机动战士交战了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 舰长点头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体在宇宙空间里 最多只能呆15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记出去前吐完肺里的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背对太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对速度匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你小子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上对方的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台新的重量级高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不适合对付高速型的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把背露给它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这样下去赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟上它的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 翻新了还是老样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那家伙占尽上风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他结束这样的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是菲利特坚持要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明白是为了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束是让他逃避战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样是为他好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是做得挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃避任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果真的为他着想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他豁出性命去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就豁出性命去跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出性命…跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢他吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话 就和他生死相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是遥控 就是自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可能是 机师潜伏在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体混身都是谜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以肯定的是 那是UE的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 话说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过武器商人亚库·多勒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚库·多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人 把那台黑色机体送到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出的报酬也数额不菲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始还兴奋了一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和其他机动战士的设计思想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差异过大让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在调查开发来源的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了一条联邦的机密情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了那台机体和联邦战斗的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明它曾经是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以联系我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中被UE利用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在没脸见人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怪我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况我们明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 武器商人竟然和UE有勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我也不知道更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果亚库·多勒受雇于UE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找出他 就能知道UE的真面目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 回到天神号上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚库·多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说向法丁倒卖机动战士设计图的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是此人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天后从法丁出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个目的地是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星托尔迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地变更
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星 明斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 请解释
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类 对UE残虐的破坏忍气吞声到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能让暴行再继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对迄今为止的数据进行分析
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得出结论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE就潜伏在附近的废弃宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可错过这次良机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰将与艾乌巴舰两艘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及扎拉姆舰两艘组成联合舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向UE据点实施攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也太蛮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和联邦军以外的私兵组编
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总司令部不可能认可！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚当斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道请告诉我们 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了前任舰长的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是疯狂的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要抽出卫星轴心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天神号牵引住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会听他的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天神号立即撤离危险的诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如果是前任舰长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉的人们现在已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我当时不知该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古鲁迪克先生做的事是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还是那个舰长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉的人会被抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个戴安·冯罗德的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实难保不会那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果没有古鲁迪克舰长的决断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号也没法战斗到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生 蜜蕾丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你做的事是严重的违纪行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为军人罪不可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已被联邦军作为叛逃者追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这一切都是为了击败UE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古鲁迪克先生的家人被UE杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨UE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使陨落之日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一切的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻女被UE所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿莎拉年仅7岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我就发誓向UE复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我们陪你去报私仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 不打算强迫大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我共同行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会被联邦军认定为叛逃者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想下船的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就下船无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算一个人也要去干翻UE！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 这场战斗会异常艰苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法保证能活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲和母亲也被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 我会和古鲁迪克先生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睁睁看着UE夺走身边的家人和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给你小子抢着说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢主动找UE麻烦的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军再大也找不到第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有通讯员 天神号寸步难行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说 我也想痛扁UE那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天神号上的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌系统反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到众多类UE移动体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 对面送上门来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:22:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来UE动真格想干掉我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吗 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起豁出性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蜂拥而至的敌人大军面前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们抛弃过节团结一心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激战之日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人的命运成就历史
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TVCM------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.44,0:24:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有脱离联邦接受机动战士改装委托的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由机械工程师联合组织
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中享有盛名的是麦德纳工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么机动战士来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会被改装成最佳状态


